com.ericbarnhill.jvcl

Class Unrolled

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ericbarnhill.jvcl.Unrolled

  • public class Unrolled
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides unrolled methods for many common convolutions. Additional unrolled methods can be generated easily using the Unroller class, added to this class and the class recompiled. This will be facilitated in future releases.
    Since:
    0.1
    Author:
    ericbarnhill
    See Also:
    Unroller
